OL,6,FDuring the trial, the court heard how
OL,7,Fa teacher raised concerns about Foden
OL,8,Fmeeting teenagers alone with Gwynedd
OL,9,FCouncil's then director of education,
OL,10,FGarem Jackson, in 2019 but the council
OL,11,Ffailed to investigate.
OL,13,FNo records of the meeting were kept.
OL,14,FMr Jackson said he was asked to speak
OL,15,Fto Foden about his behaviour, which he
OL,16,Fsaid he did.
