OL,6,FAndrew Grove & Co Solicitors in
OL,7,FCambridgeshire is now acting on behalf
OL,8,Fof potential claimants in a planned
OL,9,Fcivil lawsuit against the local
OL,10,Fauthority.
OL,12,FSolicitor Katherine Yates is appealing
OL,13,Ffor anyone who suffered emotional,
OL,14,Fpsychological, physical or sexual
OL,15,Fabuse at Foden's hands to contact them.
OL,17,FMs Yates said: "This case raises a lot
OL,18,Fof questions. There seems to be a long
OL,19,Fhistory of complaints against Foden,
OL,20,Fso why wasn't anything done sooner?
