OL,6,F"Following the criminal case and
OL,7,Fguilty verdict, the North Wales
OL,8,FSafeguarding Board has begun the work
OL,9,Fof carrying out a Children's Practice
OL,10,FReview, in accordance with Welsh
OL,11,FGovernment guidelines. The review is
OL,12,Fled by an independent chair and two
OL,13,Fexperienced reviewers.
OL,15,F"The review will bring together
OL,16,Forganisations... to identify what
OL,17,Flessons are to be learned and what
OL,18,Fimprovements need to be introduced.
